videos.description: Mikayla Pivec drains a long 3-pointer to give Oregon State their largest lead of the night at 18-13.
videos.headline: Pivec drains long 3 for Beavers

videos.description: Satou Sabally pulls off the tough shot to shorten Oregon's deficit against Oregon State.
videos.headline: Sabally gets tough shot to go in

videos.description: Aleah Goodman crosses up her defender and drains the 3-pointer for Oregon State.
videos.headline: Goodman shoots crazy 3 off slick crossover

videos.description: Destiny Slocum swishes the 3-pointer for Oregon State late as the hometown crowd goes wild.
videos.headline: Slocum hits late 3 to get hometown crowd hyped
